content:
The Vlocity Tracking Service is an event-tracking service that captures details about how Vlocity users interact with the Cards Framework. 

Typically, administrators tracing Cards Framework triggers want to track only runtime events. The Cards Framework includes a Track.CardPreview trigger for Card Designer Preview tracking entries, which can be disabled to screen out preview events.

Events tracked for the Cards Framework are OmniAnalytics Card Events, initTracking, initCardFramework, initLayout, selectCard, performAction, trackField, and Resolution.
title: Vlocity Cards Framework Event Tracking
